cdlblk.title: LOGO ILLUMINATION LIGHT COVER - Horizontal Stabilizer

remarks.para: Any number or combination may be missing. The performance decrement is negligible. (SEE FIGURE 33-45-1)

note.para: Openings created by missing light covers must be covered with Speed Tape (Permacel II or 3M425). Inspect the condition of the Speed Tape every other flight.
